text: Kanchana may refer to: ==Media== * Unicorn-Kanchana, British record label * Kanchana (1952 film), 1952 drama film produced in Telugu, Malayalam and Tamil languages * Kanchana (2011 film), Tamil horror comedy film directed by Raghava Lawrence * Kanchana (2012 TV series), a 2012 Indian Tamil-language soap opera that aired in Vijay TV * Kanchana (2015 TV series), the Tamil-language version of the Indian television series Shastri Sisters, that aired on Raj TV in 2015 ==See also== * Kanchana (name), for people with the name
